# System Architecture

## 🧠 Overview
- Frontend: HTML + CSS
- Backend: Java
- DB: Supabase

## 🗺️ Diagram
![Architecture Diagram](../images/architecture.png)

## Components
| Component   | Tech        | Role                    |
|-------------|-------------|-------------------------|
| Frontend    | HTML/CSS       | User interface          |
| Backend     | Java     | API & business logic    |
| Database    | Supabase  | Stores all data         |

## 🔒 Auth Flow
- JWT tokens
- Secure cookie storage
